name: Comput3
description: Comput3 ($COM) is offering GPU++. Scalable GPU infrastructure for Agents, Apps & Teams. With the Comput3 API, you can run inference to any open source model, video & image generation through ComfyUI and easily connect it to your end consumers. Our GPU's are cheaper than anywhere else on the market through a Global GPU sourcing algorithm. Soon, Comput3 will lower GPU costs through enabling Crypto mining farms access to our API's. The $COM token will be used to rent GPU power, Pay GPU suppliers, Discounts by Staking, and future GPU derivative markets.
